<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Product Deleted</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #444">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto">
        <header style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center">
            <h1 style="margin: 0">Product Deleted</h1>
        </header>
        <main style="padding: 20px">
            <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
            <p>
                We wanted to inform you that your product "{{productName}}" has been deleted.
            </p>
            <p>
                You have recently deleted this product from your inventory.
            </p>
            <p>
                If this was done in error, please log into your account to restore the product.
            </p>
            <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
            <p>Sincerely,</p>
            <p>SwiftMarket</p>
        </main>
        <footer style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center">
            <p style="margin: 0">&copy; 2023 Product Review. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>